summary: Badass attitude? Here\'s the warpaint to match.
descriptionHtml:
Badass Warpaint
version 1.1
by Skree000

PLEASE CHECK OUT: 
Bright Eyes (Eye texture mod)
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2464
Fountain of Youth - Beauty Project
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2535
Please endorse if you like. These are my first Skyrim mods.

Description:
Ongoing mod offering New Warpaint textures for characters. This first teaser version has an initial iteration of the \'Viper\' paint, based on the character of the same name as seen in the film Doomsday. Check back often for updates and new warpaints!

These files overwrite those located at \\skyrim\\Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\character assets\\tintmasks\\
using the following filenames:

femaleheadwarpaint_04.dds
maleheadwarpaint_04.dds

instructions:
Unpack the included files to your \\skyrim folder and it should automatically do the rest.

Credits:
Bethesda for this awesome game!
author: Skree000

files.changelogHtml: Initial release, test version of the Viper warpaint now available, female only.
